name: Crescent Bridge Canyon
description:
Introduction

Very cool canyon ending with a Natural Bridge near the mouth.

NOTE: This page covers two different canyons. The 1st canyon is Crescent Bridge and is a technical Canyon. The 2nd canyon is called Half Moon Canyon, and is mainly a non-technical canyon where scrambling is all that is required to get through it, and is not listed separately yet. But it is a worthy canyon to check out, so I am providing beta here for it.
